# =============================================================================
# GATEWAY PORT ALLOCATION - IP-BASED SYSTEM
# =============================================================================

# Port Allocation Strategy: Use last octet of IP address for port numbering
# Gateway IP Format: 10.1.32.XX where XX determines port ranges
# Port Ranges per Gateway:
#   HTTP:    8XXX  (8000 + IP octet)
#   HTTPS:   8XXX + 400 
#   GAN:     8XXX + 600
#   TRACE:   10XXX (10000 + IP octet) 
#   METRICS: 11XXX (11000 + IP octet)

# Gateway IP Addresses and Port Calculations
