# =============================================================================
# PORT OFFSET DEFINITIONS - IP-BASED SYSTEM
# =============================================================================

# Port calculation formulas based on IP address last octet:
# HTTP_PORT    = 8000 + IP_OCTET (e.g., 8051 for .51)
# HTTPS_PORT   = 8400 + IP_OCTET (e.g., 8451 for .51) 
# GAN_PORT     = 8600 + IP_OCTET (e.g., 8651 for .51)
# TRACE_PORT   = 10000 + IP_OCTET (e.g., 10051 for .51)
# METRICS_PORT = 11000 + IP_OCTET (e.g., 11051 for .51)

